body:
### Dojo Bootstrap Tour
Interactive Tour AMD module using the [Dojo Toolkit](http://www.dojotoolkit.org) and [Bootstrap](http://www.getbootstrap.com). Check out the [demo](http://kyledodge.github.io/dojo-bootstrap-tour/) or get the [code](https://github.com/kyledodge/dojo-bootstrap-tour). Pull requests are welcome :)
